data.description: Seller is motivated giving a $10,000 allowance to buy points down with an acceptable offer.   If you've dreamed of a view of the Kiamichi Mountains, this is the place for you!  This custom-built home on 30 acres is nestled at the base of the Winding Stair Mountain National Forest adjoining on two sides.  The design allows for two separate living quarters with adjoining entertaining space and options for additional bedrooms in this 3000 plus sq. ft. canvas; also features a radiant heated floor, geothermal heat, safe room, 2x6 walls, vaulted ceilings and a loft.  Property has an above ground pool and a 40 x 80 insulated shop wired with 220V.  So many possibilities for a family, amazing work from home location, vacation destination or an investment rental property; perfect for an RV park, 4-wheelers/utvs, horse back with trails behind the property. Come sit on the porch with this amazing view, watch the wildlife; deer, turkey and bear or cruise the Talimena Scenic Drive.
